OL,3,CWhat does a Police and Crime
OL,4,CCommissioner do and who's in the
OL,5,Crunning?
OL,7,FThey work with Chief Constables to
OL,8,Fhold them to account, set budgets and
OL,9,Fensure cash is spent on the right
OL,10,Fthings.
OL,12,FUltimately, they are meant to be the
OL,13,Fvoice of the public within our police
OL,14,Fforces.
OL,16,FPCCs do not have day-to-day
OL,17,Fresponsibilities of the police and
OL,18,Fthey are not involved in operational
OL,19,Fdecisions.
