OL,3,CWhat does a Police and Crime
OL,4,CCommissioner do and who's in the
OL,5,Crunning?
OL,7,FIn England, people will vote for their
OL,8,FPCC on the same day as their local
OL,9,Fcouncil. However here in Wales, local
OL,10,Felections happen .
OL,12,FYou can vote in person, via post or
OL,13,Fvia a proxy. You must have registered
OL,14,Fto vote before 16 April.
OL,16,FThis will be the first election in
OL,17,FWales that will require in person
OL,18,Fvoters to show a form of photo ID
OL,19,Fbefore casting their vote.
